.SH NAME
Mail::Box::Locker \- manage the locking of mail folders
.SH INHERITANCE
.IX Header "INHERITANCE"
.Vb 2
\& Mail::Box::Locker
\&   is a Mail::Reporter
\&
\& Mail::Box::Locker is extended by
\&   Mail::Box::Locker::DotLock
\&   Mail::Box::Locker::FcntlLock
\&   Mail::Box::Locker::Flock
\&   Mail::Box::Locker::Multi
